    <subsection>
      <title>During Class - Hour 2</title>

      <activity xml:id="sec-deriv-pt-DC-Act2">
        <statement>
          Let <m>g(x) = |x|</m>.  Recall that if <m>x \ge 0</m>, then <m>|x| = x</m>, and if <m>x \lt 0</m>, then <m>|x| = -x</m>.
          <ol marker="a.">
            <li>
              <p>
                Determine <m>g'(3)</m> and <m>g'(5)</m>.
              </p>
            </li>
